data.description:
This charming three-bedroom home is located in the sought-after Holly Hills neighborhood. With over 2,222 square feet of living space. 
Upon entry, you're greeted by a grand foyer with cove ceilings and a sweeping staircase. The main level features an open floor plan with a spacious living room, dining area, kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, pantry, island, half bath and sun porch .
The second floor houses the master suite and two additional bedrooms, all spacious and comfortable with a full bathroom. 
The finished basement provides extra living space, featuring a large family room, utility area, and a full bathroom. 
The property includes a detached two-car garage with a garage door opener for convenience. 
Situated just a third of a block from Carondelet Park, this home is conveniently located near major highways and shopping centers. This property is a must-see for buyers seeking comfort and convenience in a prime location.
